web-development.response:
JavaScript makes websites interactive! While HTML is structure and CSS is style, JavaScript is the behavior.

Real SL example: Creating a currency converter for Leones (Le) to Dollars ($):

```javascript
function convertToLeones(dollars) {
  const rate = 20000; // Example rate
  return dollars * rate;
}
```

